SCENARIO-BASED REPORT DEVELOPMENT UTILIZING DIVERSE PROMPTING TECHNIQUES – CASE STUDY 1

AIM

To develop reports using straightforward prompts, tabular prompts, and preceding question prompts.

SELECTED SCENARIO

Designing an AI-Powered Customer Support Chatbot.

PROMPTING METHODS USED

1. Straightforward Prompt
2. Tabular Format Prompting
3. Preceding Question Prompting

SAMPLE PROMPTS

Straightforward Prompt

“Design an AI chatbot for customer support with features and advantages.”

Tabular Prompt

| Feature    | Description                 |
| ---------- | --------------------------- |
| NLP        | Understand customer queries |
| Automation | Automatic responses         |

Preceding Question Prompt

“What problems do customers face in support systems? How can AI solve them?”

ANALYSIS

* Straightforward prompts gave direct answers.
* Tabular prompts improved structure.
* Preceding questions improved reasoning depth.

RESULT

Prompt structure strongly influenced response quality and organization.


